title: Andolan
subTitle: Adarsh and Aniket are two brothers who study in the same college. However, when they graduate and plan to establish a career, both of them choose different paths and gradually drift apart.

title: Qaidi
subTitle: Ravi Verma, a CBI officer, infiltrates the gang of a notorious criminal, Kali, pretending to be him. However, things take a turn when Kali regains his consciousness.

title: Bal Ganesh And The Friends From Zeba
subTitle: Three ardent followers of Bal Ganesh share the admired deity's incredible stories with their guests from the planet Zeba.

title: Dillagi
subTitle: Ranvir and Rajvir, two inseparable brothers, support each other through thick and thin. However, they find themselves in a dilemma when both of them fall in love with the same woman.

title: Hum Dil De Chuke Sanam
subTitle: A newly-wed man discovers that his wife is in love with another man and decides to unite them. Ignoring the ridicule he might have to face for this, he takes his wife to Italy in search of her love.

title: Dil Ka Rishta
subTitle: Jai, a wealthy businessman in love with Tia, accidentally kills her husband in a car crash. After the accident Tia loses her memory and falls for Jai, who struggles with guilt.

title: Hum Tumhare Hain Sanam
subTitle: Gopal is happily married to Radha until she meets her friend Suraj and starts obsessing over his singing career. Gopal suspects that they are secretly seeing each other and decides to leave her.

title: Tridev
subTitle: When an expelled police inspector, an outlaw and a commissioner's son are implicated by a dealer, they unite to seek revenge and prove they are not culprits.

title: Tango Charlie
subTitle: When the war breaks out between India and Pakistan, riots erupt in North India. Later, BSF trooper Tarun and his battalion are sent to Kargil, where they face a challenge that will decide his fate.

title: Tango Charlie
subTitle: When the war breaks out between India and Pakistan, riots erupt in North India. Later, BSF trooper Tarun and his battalion are sent to Kargil, where they face a challenge that will decide his fate.

title: Ekka Raja Rani
subTitle: Talented dancer, Barkha, saves the life of an underground crime boss, VK, who offers her a job as repayment. Later VK falls for Barkha, but she is in love with another man.

title: Mahaan
subTitle: A lawyer goes into hiding after being falsely accused of committing a crime, while his wife gives birth to twins. Years later, fate reunites the family under difficult circumstances.

title: Dharam Kanta
subTitle: A dacoit's plan goes wrong when a kidnapped child is killed after the ransom is exchanged. The boy's devastated mother curses the dacoit, who then starts to suffer the consequences of his crime.

title: Haqeeqat
subTitle: Shiva changes his name to Ajay as he leaves his criminal life after saving a police officer and his family. He falls in love with a widow and marries her, but his past comes back to haunt him.

title: Garv: Pride and Honour
subTitle: An honest officer falls prey to a corrupt system where he is dismissed from the police force for getting involved in a murder case while trying to arrest a few corrupt politicians.

title: Kyo Kii Main Jhuth Nahin Bolta
subTitle: Raj is a lawyer who finds great success with his countless fibs. However, when his son wishes for his father to stop lying, Raj is magically forced to speak the truth, which lands him in trouble.

title: Raja Hindustani
subTitle: Raja, a taxi driver, falls in love with Aarti, a rich girl and marries her against her parents' wishes. Later, her stepmother tries to create differences between the couple.

title: Adventures of Tarzan
subTitle: Ruby ventures into the forest searching for a legendary tribe but encounters Tarzan and falls for him. However, her father and fiancé plot to capture him and sell him to the circus.

title: Adventures of Tarzan
subTitle: Ruby ventures into the forest searching for a legendary tribe but encounters Tarzan and falls for him. However, her father and fiancé plot to capture him and sell him to the circus.

title: Yugpurush
subTitle: Anirudh is discharged from an asylum after 20 years of treatment. Although he still struggles to adjust to the normal world, he finds comfort with Sunita.

title: Sau Din Saas Ke
subTitle: Durga marries Prakash, unaware of his mother Bhawani Devi's dominating and abusive nature. She later insists on moving in with his family in order to teach Bhawani Devi a lesson.

title: Dil
subTitle: A father pretends to be a rich industrialist to improve his son's chances of marrying in to wealth. However, his plan backfires on him when his true identity is found out.

title: Kachche Dhaage
subTitle: Stepbrothers Aftab and Jai, who loathe each other, must learn to put aside their differences and work together to prove their innocence in a terrorism case.

title: Sapne Saajan Ke
subTitle: Shalini, who has always wanted her daughter, Jyoti, to marry a rich man, is happy that she has found Deepak to be her life partner. However, no one knows that he is only pretending to be wealthy.

title: Gharwali Baharwali
subTitle: Arun inadvertently ties the knot with Manisha and even has a child with her. He keeps this a secret from his first wife Kaajal. It is only a matter of time before his life starts to unravel.

title: Beta
subTitle: After the death of his mother, Raju's father re-marries, but his stepmother is only after the family's money. When Raju eventually marries, his wife tries to make him realise what kind of woman his stepmother is.

title: Judwaa
subTitle: Twin brothers Raja and Prem Malhotra get separated at birth but are reunited by fate to defeat Ratanlal, a local gangster, who wants to destroy the Malhotra family.
